column23: ja:"西暦2205年。「歴史修正主義者」による過去への攻撃が始まった。 歴史の改変を防ぐため、時の政府により「審神者（さにわ）」が過去に遣わされた。 審神者によって励起されたのは、刀剣に宿る付喪神「刀剣男士」。 彼らは歴史を守るため戦いへと身を投じていくのであった。 審神者から刀剣男士たちに出陣の命が下った。 蜂須賀虎徹を隊長に加州清光、大和守安定、和泉守兼定、堀川国広、長曽祢虎徹という 編成が組まれる。 蜂須賀虎徹は贋作である長曽祢虎徹の存在に反発する。 舞台は、元治元年。 歴史修正主義者の標的は――新撰組。 沖田総司の刀であった加州清光と大和守安定、土方歳三の刀であった和泉守兼定と堀川国広、 そして近藤勇の刀であった長曽祢虎徹。 かつての主を目にし、動揺する刀剣男士たち。 しかしそこに歴史修正主義者が率いる時間遡行軍の気配が迫る。 時間遡行軍の目的が分からない中、大和守安定がとった行動とは――。"}

zh:"我附身到了年纪轻轻就失去丈夫的男爵夫人‘艾莱诺·马里切’身上。 但是在原作中，关于我的描写只有四行字！ 在历经千辛万苦之后，我现在成为了当之无愧的社交界名人。 这样的我在某一天收到了令人心动的提议。 如果我能告诉男主关于女人的事情，并且帮助他像原作中那样和皇女结缘的话，我就能一夜暴富？！ 怀着激动的心情，我前往了男主‘里安’的家... “你的问题是......” “我在那晚被你迷住了” 我本来只想大干一场就离开的啊！ 被迫成为帝国绯闻制造者的艾莱诺，既心动又苦涩的故事！

column14: but not as much as my pops. \n\nOur family is a lively bunch of Tokyoites. We're also called \"Edokko\" which means \"Children of Edo\"
column15: \"Edo\" being an old name for Tokyo. \nReally
column16: it just means we've lived here a few decades from my pops and my pops' pops. \n\nSo who do we have in our humble abode? Well
column18: there's my pops. To be honest he's a bit of an oddball
column19: a \"Queer Pop\" if you will. We also got a high school student named Karin from Toyama Prefecture living with us.\n\nI don't have a mom anymore
column20: so we're not really used to any kind of \"feminine influence\" in our house.  She's a cute girl - very pretty. I'll let you in on something - It's kind of a secret. But I like to treat her like a kid calling her a \"gaki\" or rather
column21: a brat.\n\nBut sharing a roof with a pretty 16 year old girl really gets my heart pounding. My older bro's a really straight edge. Being the eldest son
column22: he gets all the responsibility and they trained him for it. He'll be getting married soon to a chick named Chitose. She's a real looker
column23: I don't know how he found her! I hope to meet her soon. \n\nThat leaves my grandma
column24: who looks like an apricot. Like one of those palmed fruit that was pickled in Edo way back when - She's three hundred years old! Despite how she looks
column25:
she's likes to play pranks and is incredibly fit. She also gets along with Karin.

Our Sesame Street's a real-life comedy set in downtown Tokyo. Players are always entering and leaving the stage. I'll introduce them when the chance comes along. 

Until then

column4: Duality is an adventure-fantasy story. But if you are looking for lovingly detailed drawings and fantastic panoramas
column5:
you will probably not (yet) be happy here.  
  
Because it is one thing above all else: An introspection; a discussion of yours truly - with me. I love to argue with myself - because I can only win.   
  
What does that mean in plain language for the story ?  
Very long and many dialogues. Less action-packed fights
column6: but more action-packed discussions!  \n  \nWhy am I doing this? On the one hand
column7: to find answers; to questions that I don't even know how I would ask
column8: and on the other - and that is much more important - to have fun. For me
column9:
telling and reading the comic is like a drug that I don't feel guilty for being addicted to.  
  
I hope to be able to conjure this effect within others through the publication.  
  
The german version is the original work and I highly recommend reading it first if you can. Because some things are bound to get „lost in translation“.
